Rating filters

Rating filters for the Rhythmbox library browser.


=== Dependencies ===

  * rhythmbox		    >= 	2.97
  * pygtk/gobject


=== Usage ===

To install, run 'install.sh' or copy the contents of the archive to 
~/.local/share/rhythmbox/plugins/RatingFilters/ and run the command 
sudo glib-compile-schemas "/usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas/".

You can set a custom favourites threshold in the plugin preferences.


